{"tid":2514940,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港全方位淪陷實例總合4(盡量每日更新)","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T14:51:47.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec97504120e4caacadcce7a465ad83294475a410","tid":2514940,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=2dabcd68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},{"pid":"bd0d3b7b38a71aa54179f8aa42567789fc94b3d7","tid":2514940,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}